{"tid":708613,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港需要更多X！","createTime":"2018-06-19T12:11:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T12:11:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"15e07cbe4a69b8e362b45ed54df55d9fee0b637d","tid":708613,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T12:11:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/陳也/daily/article/20180619/20424259\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180619%2F20424259&d=uQGCxC8pIIPMHKLX8tu5Fp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=fb43e402\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180619%2F20424259&h=57fd95ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/陳也/daily/article/20180619/20424259</a><br />\n<br />\n香港需要更多X！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180619/large/e8813a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180619%2Flarge%2Fe8813a.jpg&h=2ac3f803&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n689眼中，香港需要更多&times;&times;&times;！<br />\n<br />\n香港需要更多馬時亨。他OK市民PK，市民愈PK，689就有機會報復迫他無得連任的阿柒，賭「馬」？抵她輸甩褲。<br />\n<br />\n香港需要更多陳帆。以他的智慧，真係處理唔到。香港亂來，689蹺埋對手等住香港塌，由大灣區收返主權。689等住做大灣區第一任灣首。<br />\n<br />\n香港需要更多維園。689這個阿伯轉舞台，踢走真維園阿伯，佔領維園做KOL，爽。<br />\n香港需要更多龍門。唔係葉鴻輝，係齋龍門，方便689搬，目標係搬八萬五個！<br />\n<br />\n香港需要更多龍蝦。為了照顧家庭，689落台後在家養龍蝦，變身成專家。將來升呢做埋大廚，落重手煮初一暴動菜，佢請客，市民會鈔。<br />\n<br />\n香港需要更多蘋果日報。689得閒到痹，冇job冇所事事唯有刨報紙、鋤編輯。蘋果遲遲唔出午報晚報，躁狂689遲早發癲！癲狼取代戰狼，習總點讚！  <br />\n<br />\n陳也 <br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n廢物利用 (尊子)"}]}